snippet.title: Character Teaser - "Kamisato Ayaka: The Homeward Heron" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
The Yashiro Commission is responsible for the sacred matters and cultural affairs of Inazuma. The Shirasagi Himegimi handles various official duties with dignified poise.
However, when the Heron returns home, she is back to being simply Ayaka, a girl whose true desire remains hidden within her heart.
But this time, I'm in your company, Traveler. My wish may soon come true.
